snippet.title: The Addams Family Mansion Mayhem - Announce Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: They’re creepy, they’re kooky, and their home is in danger! Save the Addams Family Mansion from destruction in this hilarious 3D platform adventure for up to four players #TheAddamsFamily #MansionMayhem arrives this Halloween!
